    "Thus, FRoGS vectors are widely applicable to biomedical problems beyond drug target identification including identifying risk genes of diseases 27, uncovering diseasedisease relationships 70, and single cell clustering and classification 71.",
    "We hypothesize one reason that preventing deep learning models from further enhancing the target recall relates to the fact that both transcriptional profiling data and compound activity profiles generally capture the downstream effect of a compound/shRNA/cDNA on its target pathway.",
